  -high/low_sentiment_threshold
  -margin_boost_max: 0.5
  +compute_margin_multiplier(direction, sentiment): float
}

INewsSource <|.. CryptoCompareNewsSource
INewsSource <|.. DDGNewsSource
ISentimentAnalyzer <|.. OpenAISentimentAnalyzer
ISentimentAnalyzer <|.. GeminiSentimentAnalyzer
IMarginAdjuster <|.. SentimentMarginAdjuster
NewsEngine --> INewsSource
NewsEngine --> ISentimentAnalyzer

note bottom of SentimentMarginAdjuster
  LONG + bullish (>0.75) → margin ×(1+boost)
  SHORT + bearish (<0.25) → margin ×(1+boost)
  otherwise → ×1.0 (no change).
  Sizing boost, **not** signal gating.
end note

